 Hard to Be a God is a role playing game with adventure and espionage 
 elements based on a storyline of the novel with the same name by the 
 Strugatsky brothers.

 The main hero is a graduate of a medieval secret service highschool. His 
 mission is to scout and report the situation in the Kingdom of Arcanar, an 
 indepented anarchical state. The character is a real professional who took 
 the best course in combat and diplomatic training. He's strong, sly and 
 intelligent, he's mightier than the whole Arcanar, but his world still has 
 some surprises for him.

 The highly developed Earth race governs the series of unexpected events in 
 Ancanar and contacts the agent. The main hero starts his new mission in 
 co-operation with Earth forces. The agent gains access to incredibly
